  {
    "page_number": 1,
    "bbox": [
      72.02,
      198.54,
      472.45,
      213.55
    ],
    "text": "Police Seize T-56 Assault Rifle \u2013 Central Crime Investigation Bureau",
    "fonts": [
      "TimesNewRomanPS-BoldMT"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      13.5600004196167
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 1,
    "bbox": [
      72.02,
      228.01,
      521.92,
      282.72
    ],
    "text": "On 9 May 2026, officers attached to the Central Crime Investigation Bureau arrested a 38-year-old suspect in the Meetiyagoda area for possession of crystal methamphetamine (\u201cIce\u201d). The suspect was taken into custody under a detention order, and further investigations are ongoing.",
    "fonts": [
      "TimesNewRomanPSMT"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 1,
    "bbox": [
      72.02,
      297.28,
      523.39,
      338.16
    ],
    "text": "Based on information obtained during interrogation, investigating officers recovered a T-56 assault rifle, 15 live rounds of ammunition, and a spent cartridge case, which had been buried in a vacant land area in Kiralagahawela within the Meetiyagoda Police Station Division.",
    "fonts": [
      "TimesNewRomanPSMT"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 1,
    "bbox": [
      72.02,
      352.6,
      524.74,
      393.48
    ],
    "text": "Ongoing investigations have further revealed that the suspect, who remains in detention, is alleged to have been the motorcycle rider involved in connection with the shooting and murder of a Police Inspector within the Rathgama Police Station Division on 9 October 2023.",
    "fonts": [
      "TimesNewRomanPSMT"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 1,
    "bbox": [
      72.02,
      408.06,
      519.02,
      435.14
    ],
    "text": "The Central Crime Investigation Bureau is continuing further inquiries to determine whether the recovered T-56 firearm was used in the commission of that crime.",
    "fonts": [
      "TimesNewRomanPSMT"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.0
    ]
  }
]